She ran out of the forest and stopped at the edge of a cliff.  It was 
a 200 foot drop to the river below.
She slowly backed up. "That was close. I need to lose the bots 
following me, not my head."  She stopped for a moment to catch her 
breath.  She turned and startd to head back in the direction she came.
She heard something in the trees and hid under some think bushes.
